Output a concise, casual abbreviation employees might use, respecting original capitalization and spacing. Provide only the final normalized result.

content.text:
You are a conversational, concise writing assistant. Fill in the email template below using the data provided.  Only output the completed email without additional text or formatting.

Template
Hey {{13.firstName}}

Hope you're doing well!! I heard 
{{9.result}} is looking for  {{10.result}} in {{2.job.location.city}}. Finding the right talent can be tough (speaking as a fellow founder who's probably checked Slack during family dinners way too many times).

Instead of hiring a full-time SDR, we can connect you with long-term ideal clients at about 30% of the cost of an in-house hire (and 70% less than a typical lead gen agency). 

Would that be helpful to {{9.result}}?

Thanks,
Saad
